With the start of the Australian Open approaching next week, Watson told BBC Sport: 'This is how I want to play consistently. 

'I'm feeling good, confident and very comfortable coming to the net.'

Kurumi Nara ended Johanna Larsson's challenge with a 7-6 (7/1) 6-4 triumph and the Japanese will now challenge either third seed Camila Giorgi or Kaia Kanepi for a semi-final place. 

